arts.ttl: Messi’s multi-goal streak ends in Inter Miami’s 3-0 loss to FC Cincinnati
arts.sum: Lionel Messi’s MLS-record streak of scoring multiple goals in five straight matches ended on Wednesday night in Inter Miami’s 3-0 loss to FC Cincinnati. The loss ended a five-match winning streak for Inter Miami (11-4-5) which is fifth in the Eastern Conference standings.

arts.ttl: FC Cincinnati vs. Inter Miami CF: Preview, Predictions and Lineups
arts.sum: Inter Miami face their toughest challenge since returning from the Club World Cup when they travel to face FC Cincinnati.
